description:
Always full of stories, Quincy Jones played the game of Qwest TV's flash interview with spirit, making it special, of course. For example, in identifying the best song to make love to, he replied: "There are so many," with a twinkle in his eyes, before telling us that Nat King Cole's songs were very effective for that particular pursuit. 

Watch more great music curated by Quincy Jones & his team: https://qwest.tv/
